        "# 04 · RLHF Data & Reward Model Training\n",
        "**DS-GA 3001 · RLHF Portfolio Management**  \n",
        "**Final version:** `04_rlhf_data_v3.ipynb`\n",
        "1. **Task 8** — Generate preference pair dataset from base agent rollouts (Ziyang)\n",
        "2. **Task 10** — Train 3 MLP reward models with Bradley-Terry loss (Wynnian)\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
        "\n",
        "Builds the RLHF preference dataset and trains the persona-specific reward models used by the final fine-tuning stage.\n",
        "\n",
        "**What this notebook does:**\n",
        "1. Generates trajectory windows from the best base PPO agent.\n",
        "2. Constructs preference pairs for three personas: conservative, balanced, and aggressive.\n",
        "3. Trains one MLP reward model per persona using Bradley-Terry loss.\n",
        "4. Saves the final reward-model artifacts and normalization statistics used by `05_finetuning_v5.ipynb`.\n",
         "\n",
        "**Input:** `base_agent_seed2.zip`, `features_train.parquet`, `features_val.parquet`, helper code from `src/`  \n",
        "**Output:** `preferences.parquet`, `reward_model_{conservative,balanced,aggressive}_v5.pt`, `{persona}_v5_norm_stats.npz`, reward-model diagnostic figures\n"
      ]
    },
